title: Red Dwarf series 7
description:
Classic cult TV program red Dwarf series 7 - British comedy at its best. Lister, Kryten, Cat, Rimmer and Kochanski continue their search for Red Dwarf. 

Includes:
All 7 regular episodes, Tikka to ride remastered and extended, Duct soup extended.

Extras:

Smeg ups, Deleted scenes, easter eggs, trailers, Identity Within - the episode that never became, Back from the Dead documentry, and various CGI shots.

Encoded in .mkv using lame mp3 and ms-MPEG4-V2. I recommend you use VLC media player to play or covertxtodvd to burn. You may need to download codec. Google is your freind.
